    "As shown on the left-hand side of Fig. 5, the AUROC score of our method is much higher than the baselines.",
    "Particularly, the confidence-based method and energybased model perform only marginally better than random guess (AUROC = 0.5) on the MNIST and Fashion MNIST datasets.",
